cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves enhancing feature representations, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.LG). The use of a hand-crafted mechanism also suggests a focus on model design and architecture (cs.NE). Finally, the experiments involve benchmark datasets, which are commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
